articles.title: Dune: Part Two, Aquaman 2 and The Color Purple may be pushed into 2024 - Daily Mail
articles.description: Warner Bros. is considering pushing three of its biggest movies slated for the end of this year into 2024, amid the dual strikes from the Writers Guild of America (WGA) and SAG-AFTRA.
